{"tid":1566003,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"再譯《我願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-13T11:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:56:40.000Z","uid":127479,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a428fdeb01f646934120e0076f659e71445d55","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"［代友post]<br />\n尋晚終於聽咗榮光嘅交響樂團版本，覺得好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己對翻譯有啲興趣，所以膽粗粗譯咗個歌詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoUIDL4SB60g&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88t8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=71902b69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g</a> <br />\n<br />\n之前都見有巴打出咗英譯本，但係我都有啲諗法，想譯多一個版本：<br />\n<br />\n一）部份譯詞與旋律節奏不太合，有些位置詞語被樂句切斷；想配合樂句寫個稍微好唱點的版本<br />\n<br />\n二）部份譯詞用字不完美，可接受，有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n三）有幾篇水準甚高，例如七劍巴嘅高汁 &quot;Glory be to thee, Hong Kong&quot;<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1</a><br />\n但係超出咗原詞結構和意思；當然呢種情況可以話已取其意，可忘其形；但是個人都還是有少少執著表現出原本結構的威力<br />\n亦都是自己每次見到著迷既作品會想譯既原因<br />\n<br />\n於是就誕生咗下面嘅版本，算係希望最忠於中文原詞意象嘅成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《我願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><em><strong>Glory unto Hong Kong</strong></em></span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">For whom is the land wrought in tears</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">For what do our hearts burn with rage</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Lift your heads, hush no more</span><br />\n吶喊聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Let our cries pierce forth</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Liberty unto this place</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">How deep is the heart wrought with fear</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">And still how we stand, fast and strong</span><br />\n何解 血在流<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Though our blood be shed</span><br />\n但邁進聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Our songs of march press on</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Till we build our bright Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">As the stars subside, the night befalls</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹來 號角聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">From across the mist there comes a shrill of horns</span><br />\n捍自由<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Fend our rights</span><br />\n來齊集這裡<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Together we fight </span><br />\n來全力抗對<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Courage and wisdom be our guide</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Our dawn has come, now to arms! Free Hong Kong!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Justice shall come! Revolution of our time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Long live liberty and democracy</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Glory unto Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n都無期望有人會唱（除非自己出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），但發夢希望有得推到俾DGX巴團隊見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考慮下用作英文版翻譯，不過咁大想頭我都係諗下好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85690af3516a95ce0ec14e84e2c10f6849b44e69","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c01b3bc538a4254c6dc7b462e5459e52c4178e7","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0c86af83a8648b4deb4aa21c28b12dcb86b097","tid":1566003,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月15日見！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Trzyi1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrzyi1f.jpg&h=f89f6e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04bde7b7aed02da02d792fa13aaabdfc087ad242","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a465de57467ec3693a9014a2c754ce28eb640e0","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd39636e4004465436c12a32e2560cace797404a","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd0c86af83a8648b4deb4aa21c28b12dcb86b097","tid":1566003,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月15日見！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Trzyi1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrzyi1f.jpg&h=f89f6e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21aa8a248ef0a568dfacfbb7f3d7ca0aaa7dddc7","tid":1566003,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌啲中秋icon 好正"},{"pid":"6